<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">ح ذ ل:</span> <span class="c2">(الْحُذْلُ)</span> بِوَزْنِ الْقُفْلِ حَاشِيَةُ الْإِزَارِ وَالْقَمِيصِ.<span class="c5"> وَفِي الْحَدِيثِ:</span> <span class="c2">«هَاتِي حُذْلَكِ، فَجَعَلَ فِيهِ الْمَالَ»</span> .<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>